      \hline
     & Category & {N, genes} & R$^{2}$ $_{AS ,Alu}$ & one-tailed p$_{AS}$ & R$^{2}$  $_{S ,Alu}$ & one-tailed p$_{S}$ \\ 
      \hline
    1 & Housekeeping & 2237 & -0.96 & 5.34e-06& -0.40 & 0.126\\  
      2 & Neutrophil & 231 & -0.76 & 5.37e-03 &-0.21 & 0.280 \\ 
      3 & Muscle & 111 & -0.53 & 0.058 & 0.02& 0.478 \\ 
      4 & Cartilage & 133 & -0.53 &  0.058 & 0.23 & 0.258 \\ 
      5 & Testis & 252 & -0.51 & 0.066 & -0.38 & 0.139 \\ 
      6 & Liver & 305 & -0.43 & 0.107 & -0.22 & 0.270\\ 
